{"tid":1783302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次搭的士搭到想喊","createTime":"2019-12-14T16:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T19:18:17.000Z","uid":123890,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5d9b238fa55820e583dd8a4f35f1a1b5fa9f8c","tid":1783302,"uid":123890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"話說今日遲左出門口 所以要搭的士到目的地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我     <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />的士狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔該想去xxx<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 下 你唔係去旺角方向咖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔係 唔該車我去xxx<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你唔係去旺角方向既話就係對面搭車啦 對面都有的士啦<br />\n<br />\n個時我真係好趕 唔想同佢嘈 所以我冇回佢<br />\n之後佢就車我去xxx個方向<br />\n途中一直俾說話我聽 又話咩唔順路 又話唔識去xxx<br />\n我個時真係好嬲 但我真係好趕所以我唔敢駁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咁究竟點去啊 係咪行呢條路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (因為我都唔識路) 咁你直接放我係秀茂坪落啦<br />\n<br />\n之後去到觀塘翠屏 個的士佬就停左係一條斜路下面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 呢到係xxx啦 (但根本同我目的地差成十分鐘車程)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你上呢條斜路就到啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 下 我唔識路喎 (之後就停左架車係路邊 個個位根本唔係落客位 佢都冇諗住開車)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你行呢條路就到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (冇反應 繼續唔開車)<br />\n隔左幾秒個的士佬就叫我係到落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個下真係好想喊 超趕時間仲要俾人趕落車<br />\n個仆街一開始想拒載 全程俾說話我聽<br />\n最後仲要冇車到我去目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位有冇投訴方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0f05bcfae9cbe172b6e405949e18bf5860aa8f","tid":1783302,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"275c61dea39a666985c457d65c4e8f3a2be3b2ec","tid":1783302,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"uber la"},{"pid":"0bfb94be09cf75009f8256a4773cc959a76c7384","tid":1783302,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"唔好比錢"},{"pid":"1b7c247091f9374ef4f62e1d2d9439bfee15d553","tid":1783302,"uid":194894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"無 建議你下次發癲係佢架車嘔 之後擺低車費走人"},{"pid":"8c8d788d37903a2e6dc6b924475510124c7349b8","tid":1783302,"uid":301911,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"又要嬲又要打晒交叉 想點？"},{"pid":"ef3fd567c60bce09217c9cf83e31d5d2ba179b7f","tid":1783302,"uid":204401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"唔好比錢走啦"},{"pid":"6a73329556ba0bdb925b241ccbe0f30e9a365909","tid":1783302,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"你廢"},{"pid":"357c90a6d6007a0066e812c82e415591f813177d","tid":1783302,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"你唔畀錢<br />\n你睇下佢會唔會唔車你去目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b972151963bdb61262889f76d67fb36feb2b3a5","tid":17833